title: 12/21: Start or Sit (NFC); RB Injuries (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
We've got a "Good Luck Player" for you to put on your squads if you've got the open roster space (2:28), and we've got players we think might win us Week 16 and those who might lose us Week 16 (4:10) ... Plenty of news and notes (8:13) as we check in on some RB situations and key injuries on the defensive side of the ball. Then we've got the Startometer (16:50) for Tevin Coleman, Dante Pettis, Dak Prescott, David Johnson and others ... KC-SEA (26:00), PIT-NO (34:15), HOU-PHI (41:10), MIN-DET (48:00), TB-DAL (52:10), CHI-SF (55:15), ATL-CAR (1:00:00), LAR-ARI (1:03:00) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
 
To learn more about listener data and our privacy practices visit: https://www.audacyinc.com/privacy-policy
